# Worker Loop: knowledge-stale-loop

Parent: `llm-wiki-mission-loop`

## Goal

Evidence hash changes must mark knowledge cards stale before fast path returns cached answers.

## Read before touching code

1. `docs/knowledge-stale-auto/14-implementation-plan.zh.md`
2. `docs/knowledge-stale-auto/15-verification-plan.zh.md`
3. `state/phase.md`

## Iterate

1. State which N1 phase gate (G1–G3) this change advances.
2. Smallest diff; one primary variable per PR.
3. Verify:

```bash
npm run typecheck
npm test -- tests/knowledge-fast-path tests/knowledge
npm run knowledge:refresh-stale   # after Phase 2 lands
npm test
```

## Stop signals

Use `done` when gate commands for the touched phase pass.
Use `blocked-needs-human` for product scope changes outside N1.
